{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 2,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 326.069,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.529,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, it came to pass that the Lord spake unto my father,",
      "verse": "2:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.709,
      "end": 6.263,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even in a dream, and said unto him:",
      "verse": "2:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 6.443,
      "end": 8.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Blessed art thou Lehi,",
      "verse": "2:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.434,
      "end": 10.71,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the things which thou hast done;",
      "verse": "2:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 10.89,
      "end": 13.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and because thou hast been faithful",
      "verse": "2:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 13.299,
      "end": 17.2,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and declared unto this people the things which I commanded thee,",
      "verse": "2:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.38,
      "end": 19.841,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, they seek to take away thy life.",
      "verse": "2:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.521,
      "end": 24.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord commanded my father, even in a dream,",
      "verse": "2:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 25.113,
      "end": 26.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he should take his family",
      "verse": "2:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 27.011,
      "end": 29.519,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and depart into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "2:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 30.199,
      "end": 35.029,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he was obedient unto the word of the Lord,",
      "verse": "2:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 35.209,
      "end": 38.042,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore he did as the Lord commanded him.",
      "verse": "2:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 38.722,
      "end": 42.669,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he departed into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "2:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 42.849,
      "end": 45.635,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he left his house, and the land of his inheritance,",
      "verse": "2:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 45.815,
      "end": 47.858,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his gold, and his silver,",
      "verse": "2:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 48.038,
      "end": 50.685,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his precious things, and took nothing with him,",
      "verse": "2:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 50.865,
      "end": 52.583,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it were his family,",
      "verse": "2:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 52.763,
      "end": 55.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and provisions, and tents,",
      "verse": "2:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 55.219,
      "end": 57.355,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and departed into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "2:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 58.035,
      "end": 60.125,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he came down by the borders",
      "verse": "2:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 60.305,
      "end": 62.441,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "near the shore of the Red Sea;",
      "verse": "2:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 62.621,
      "end": 65.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he traveled in the wilderness",
      "verse": "2:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 65.309,
      "end": 68.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the borders which are nearer the Red Sea;",
      "verse": "2:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 68.647,
      "end": 72.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he did travel in the wilderness with his family,",
      "verse": "2:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 72.496,
      "end": 75.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which consisted of my mother, Sariah,",
      "verse": "2:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 75.277,
      "end": 78.853,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my elder brothers, who were Laman, Lemuel, and Sam.",
      "verse": "2:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 79.533,
      "end": 84.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when he had traveled three days in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "2:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 84.403,
      "end": 88.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he pitched his tent in a valley by the side of a river of water.",
      "verse": "2:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 88.891,
      "end": 92.374,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he built an altar of stones,",
      "verse": "2:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 92.554,
      "end": 94.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and made an offering unto the Lord,",
      "verse": "2:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 94.824,
      "end": 97.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and gave thanks unto the Lord our God.",
      "verse": "2:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 97.872,
      "end": 101.494,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he called the name of the river, Laman,",
      "verse": "2:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 101.674,
      "end": 103.95,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it emptied into the Red Sea;",
      "verse": "2:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 104.13,
      "end": 107.659,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the valley was in the borders near the mouth thereof.",
      "verse": "2:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 108.339,
      "end": 111.961,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when my father saw that the waters of the river",
      "verse": "2:9",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 112.141,
      "end": 116.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "emptied into the fountain of the Red Sea, he spake unto Laman, saying:",
      "verse": "2:9",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 116.315,
      "end": 119.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O that thou mightest be like unto this river,",
      "verse": "2:9",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 119.514,
      "end": 123.369,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "continually running into the fountain of all righteousness!",
      "verse": "2:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 124.049,
      "end": 126.092,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also spake unto Lemuel:",
      "verse": "2:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 126.272,
      "end": 129.198,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O that thou mightest be like unto this valley,",
      "verse": "2:10",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 129.378,
      "end": 132.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "firm and steadfast, and immovable",
      "verse": "2:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 132.252,
      "end": 134.574,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in keeping the commandments of the Lord!",
      "verse": "2:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 135.254,
      "end": 140.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now this he spake because of the stiffneckedness of Laman and Lemuel;",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 140.217,
      "end": 144.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold they did murmur in many things against their father,",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 144.902,
      "end": 147.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because he was a visionary man,",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 147.358,
      "end": 150.609,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and had led them out of the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 150.789,
      "end": 153.157,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to leave the land of their inheritance,",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 153.337,
      "end": 158.445,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their gold, and their silver, and their precious things,",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 158.625,
      "end": 160.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to perish in the wilderness.",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 160.616,
      "end": 162.613,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And this they said he had done",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 162.793,
      "end": 165.765,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the foolish imaginations of his heart.",
      "verse": "2:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 166.445,
      "end": 169.556,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus Laman and Lemuel, being the eldest,",
      "verse": "2:12",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 169.736,
      "end": 171.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did murmur against their father.",
      "verse": "2:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 172.006,
      "end": 174.839,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they did murmur because they knew not",
      "verse": "2:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 175.019,
      "end": 178.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the dealings of that God who had created them.",
      "verse": "2:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 178.857,
      "end": 180.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Neither did they believe",
      "verse": "2:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 180.662,
      "end": 184.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that Jerusalem, that great city, could be destroyed",
      "verse": "2:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 184.65,
      "end": 186.879,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of the prophets.",
      "verse": "2:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 187.059,
      "end": 190.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they were like unto the Jews who were at Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "2:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 190.861,
      "end": 194.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who sought to take away the life of my father.",
      "verse": "2:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 194.931,
      "end": 198.228,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that my father did speak unto them",
      "verse": "2:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 198.408,
      "end": 202.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the valley of Lemuel, with power, being filled with the Spirit,",
      "verse": "2:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 202.721,
      "end": 205.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until their frames did shake before him.",
      "verse": "2:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 205.362,
      "end": 207.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he did confound them,",
      "verse": "2:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 207.26,
      "end": 209.721,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they durst not utter against him;",
      "verse": "2:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 209.901,
      "end": 212.455,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they did as he commanded them.",
      "verse": "2:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 213.135,
      "end": 215.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my father dwelt in a tent.",
      "verse": "2:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 215.858,
      "end": 219.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, being exceedingly young,",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 219.66,
      "end": 222.168,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless being large in stature,",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 222.348,
      "end": 226.203,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also having great desires to know of the mysteries of God,",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 226.383,
      "end": 228.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I did cry unto the Lord;",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 228.885,
      "end": 230.928,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold he did visit me,",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 231.108,
      "end": 234.359,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did soften my heart that I did believe all the words",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 234.539,
      "end": 236.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which had been spoken by my father;",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 237.134,
      "end": 240.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I did not rebel against him like unto my brothers.",
      "verse": "2:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 241.297,
      "end": 242.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I spake unto Sam,",
      "verse": "2:17",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 243.102,
      "end": 245.331,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "making known unto him the things",
      "verse": "2:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 245.511,
      "end": 248.994,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the Lord had manifested unto me by his Holy Spirit.",
      "verse": "2:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 249.174,
      "end": 252.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he believed in my words.",
      "verse": "2:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 252.78,
      "end": 257.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, behold, Laman and Lemuel would not hearken unto my words;",
      "verse": "2:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 257.743,
      "end": 260.901,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and being grieved because of the hardness of their hearts",
      "verse": "2:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 261.081,
      "end": 262.985,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I cried unto the Lord for them.",
      "verse": "2:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 263.665,
      "end": 266.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "2:19",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 267.049,
      "end": 268.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Blessed art thou, Nephi,",
      "verse": "2:19",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 269.04,
      "end": 270.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of thy faith,",
      "verse": "2:19",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 270.799,
      "end": 273.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thou hast sought me diligently,",
      "verse": "2:19",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 273.44,
      "end": 275.158,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with lowliness of heart.",
      "verse": "2:19",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 275.838,
      "end": 278.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And inasmuch as ye shall keep my commandments,",
      "verse": "2:20",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 278.851,
      "end": 280.151,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall prosper,",
      "verse": "2:20",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 280.331,
      "end": 282.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall be led to a land of promise;",
      "verse": "2:20",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 282.74,
      "end": 285.991,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even a land which I have prepared for you; yea,",
      "verse": "2:20",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 286.171,
      "end": 289.329,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a land which is choice above all other lands.",
      "verse": "2:20",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 290.009,
      "end": 293.213,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And inasmuch as thy brethren shall rebel against thee,",
      "verse": "2:21",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 293.393,
      "end": 296.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be cut off from the presence of the Lord.",
      "verse": "2:21",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 297.324,
      "end": 300.528,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And inasmuch as thou shalt keep my commandments,",
      "verse": "2:22",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 300.708,
      "end": 304.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thou shalt be made a ruler and a teacher over thy brethren.",
      "verse": "2:22",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 304.917,
      "end": 307.982,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, in that day that they shall rebel against me,",
      "verse": "2:23",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 308.162,
      "end": 310.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will curse them even with a sore curse,",
      "verse": "2:23",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 310.989,
      "end": 313.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall have no power over thy seed",
      "verse": "2:23",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 313.77,
      "end": 316.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "except they shall rebel against me also.",
      "verse": "2:23",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 317.004,
      "end": 319.744,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if it so be that they rebel against me,",
      "verse": "2:24",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 319.924,
      "end": 322.618,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be a scourge unto thy seed,",
      "verse": "2:24",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 322.798,
      "end": 325.399,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to stir them up in the ways of remembrance.",
      "verse": "2:24",
      "lineIndex": 107
    }
  ]
}